        <ul>
          <li>
            ðŸ“§ <strong>Email:</strong>
            <a href="mailto:legionwikiofficial@gmail.com"
              >legionwikiofficial@gmail.com</a
            >
          </li>
          <li>ðŸ’¬ <strong>Discord:</strong> <code>@yichi</code></li>
          <li>
            ðŸŽ® <strong>In-Game:</strong> Message <code>yichi</code> in BAR
